  "Say": {
    "_dirName": "Say",
    "_dirType": "sub",
    "0": {
      "_dirName": "0",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "Hmm... If you really need this, you should give back the things that #p218# took. Then, I will give the #b#t4031064##k to you."
      },
      "1": {
        "_dirName": "1",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "How about it? Would you like to pay it back and take it with you? Of course, the things #p218# borrowed were all… very precious, you know..."
      },
      "yes": {
        "_dirName": "yes",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Really? You must be really close to #p218#. Anyway, okay. I need #b1 #t4001007#, 1 #t4020108#, and 30 #t4000039##k. I spent years collecting all these and #p218# just took them all!!! "
        },
        "1": {
          "_dirName": "1",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Well... If you give these back to me, I will definitely give you the #b#t4031064##k in return. Oh! The #b#t4001007##k is probably being held by #r#o49#s#k."
        }
      },
      "no": {
        "_dirName": "no",
        "_dirType": "sub",
        "0": {
          "_dirName": "0",
          "_dirType": "String",
          "_value": "Okay. You don't have to pay the debt when you weren't the borrower. Anyway, please tell #p218# that if she wants to get the cape back, she should return the things she took from me."
        }
      }
    },
    "1": {
      "_dirName": "1",
      "_dirType": "sub",
      "0": {
        "_dirName": "0",
        "_dirType": "String",
        "_value": "M-my things! I thought I'd never see them again! Take the #b#t4031064##k back, as we promised!"
